OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShoplifting an epidemic,   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsays John Lewis boss       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Shoplifting has become an "epidemic" in
OL,6, the past year, the boss of John Lewis, 
OL,7, Dame Sharon White, has told the BBC.   
OL,9,FShe told the Today programme the       
OL,10,Fretailer had seen offences double over 
OL,11,Fthe past 12 months.                    
OL,13,FDame Sharon said it was also "not      
OL,14,Fright" that shop workers were "having  
OL,15,Fto put up with abuse and attacks".     
OL,17,FA group of retailers, including John   
OL,18,FLewis, have agreed to fund a police    
OL,19,Foperation to crack down on shoplifting,
OL,20,Fcalled "Project Pegasus".              
